responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "7657B09841296A5713AE699B962D9A88", "They are godkin, like you. They call themselves Sighted, but we of the Ashen Flame know them to be misled. The gods have abandoned your people, they languish in the twilight of this world. We are ascendant now, but these Sighted attempt to cling to some semblance of power by scrabbling in the ruins of your kinds\' past triumphs. They are fallen, lost, but they do not realize.")
